ass=\"toc-text\">5. 有长尾商业价值的产品形态更好</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%89%E3%80%81%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">三、商业模式</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">企业家的分类</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%BB%99%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E4%BC%B0%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">如何给企业估值？</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B8%82%E5%87%80%E7%8E%87%EF%BC%88%E7%89%87%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">市净率（片面）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B8%82%E7%9B%88%E7%8E%87%EF%BC%88PE-PEG%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%88%E7%89%87%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">市盈率（PE&#x2F;PEG）（片面）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%8E%B0%E9%87%91%E6%B5%81%EF%BC%88%E7%89%87%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">现金流（片面）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B0%86%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%88%E5%88%A9%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF%E5%89%8D%E6%99%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">将来的盈利以及增长前景</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">最佳投资时间</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E5%8F%8D%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%9A%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%A9%E6%B6%A6%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. 反例：规模上升，利润下降。</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%A9%E6%B6%A6%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%